    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      151.25,
      526.4,
      164.29
    ],
    "text": "According to the order dated 16.06.2023, the learned High Court Judge observed that the",
