      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      338.0,
      526.51,
      351.04
    ],
    "text": "The conduct of the Petitioner is a pertinent factor in the determination of this application.",
