    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      399.7,
      526.2,
      412.74
    ],
    "text": "In any event, revision is a discretionary remedy and the conduct of the defendant is a",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      419.5,
      526.33,
      432.54
    ],
    "text": "matter which is intensely relevant. I hold that the conduct of the defendant disentitles",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      439.3,
      456.29,
      452.34
    ],
    "text": "him to relief by way of revision in the facts and circumstances of this case.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      479.02,
      526.15,
      492.06
    ],
    "text": "For the foregoing reasons, I hold that the petitioner is not entitled to invoke the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      498.82,
      263.88,
      511.86
    ],
    "text": "revisionary jurisdiction of this court.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
